rategic plans.</p><p></p><p> <strong>A default cycle has started, and markets are not paying attention.</strong><br /> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/defaultcycle.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-318997" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/defaultcycle.png" alt="" width="700" height="299" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/defaultcycle.png 1066w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/defaultcycle-300x128.png 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/defaultcycle-1024x437.png 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/defaultcycle-768x328.png 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/defaultcycle-250x107.png 250w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></a><br /> Source: Torsten Slok, Apollo Global</p><p></p><p> <a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://mailchi.mp/005fb77d75b9/ritholtzreads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>Sign up for our reads-only mailing list here</em></a> .</p><p></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/09/10-friday-am-reads-421/">10 Friday AM Reads</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com">The Big Picture</a> .</p> ;
